Package: napd
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-dbus, python3-gi
Recommends: power-profiles-daemon
Maintainer: metallcorn <metallcorn@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/metallcorn/napd
Description: Focus-aware power manager for Linux (user-space App Nap)
 napd watches the focused window on KDE Plasma (Wayland) and throttles
 background CPU hogs via cgroup v2, releasing them instantly on focus.
 It protects apps using the camera, microphone or audio, only throttles
 on battery, and reports per-app power. All user-space, no root daemon.
